README
======

Requirements:
------------
 
* libxml, version 2.2.8 or later (http://xmlsoft.org/, ftp://xmlsoft.org)
* libdb2, the Berkeley database library 2.7.7, it comes with many recent
  Linux distributions, but please make sure it is 2.7.7!
* You need the XOSD library if you want to enjoy the cool on-screen
  display, this is optional. But if you want it, please use 0.6.1 or
  above. It can be downloaded at http://www.ignavus.net/software.html

For more info, please consult the manpage.
